{"tid":811533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【慈母full pay】荃灣91呎劏房48萬成交 呎價5,275元平過公屋","createTime":"2018-09-09T02:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T02:53:39.000Z","uid":208074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"169f63bbc46ccdf31525b97c2898b553c9398770","tid":811533,"uid":208074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:05:20.000Z","msg":"樓市回調之際，不少二手屋苑出現劈價情況，近日有荃灣分契劏房48萬元成交，成交價平絕全港私樓。中原地產林經略表示，荃灣川龍街67號唐樓5字樓，樓齡近50年，其中一個實用面積只得91方呎的分契劏房戶，現時月租3,500元，連租約以48萬成交，呎價5,275元，成交價比不少未補地價的公、居屋要低，料為全港最平私樓。<br />\n據悉，買家是約20歲的年青上車客，由於單位樓齡太舊普遍銀行無法承造按揭，而且單位總價低，是次由其母親「full pay」購入贈兒子作自住用。資料指，該唐樓樓齡近50年，一層設兩伙，於1984年時已分契將一個單位劏成5伙，而是次成交的單位，上手業主於1996年僅以10萬元買入，是次轉手單位升值38萬元或近3倍。<br />\n由市場提供的單位片段可見，91方呎的細單位滿佈現租客的個人物品，令空間更感狹窄，屋內站了2人後已難以走動。而牆身油漆及窗花亦出現不少污漬及崩花。另外單位設有窗戶，外望附近一帶舊唐樓景。"},{"pid":"8eee0a178da3e27384fba924b27490870c8e1a36","tid":811533,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/09/101340_89f6c374beccf878730170970bc5a152.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2F101340_89f6c374beccf878730170970bc5a152.gif&h=4ff45171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n福氣來㗎 香港人"},{"pid":"aefaa5de814afde3bc9feeb477ec88f215fc1997","tid":811533,"uid":77473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:27:37.000Z","msg":"買九十呎舊樓畀個仔自住<br />\n伯母一定餓左好耐"},{"pid":"139eac90598330274cfa96676b6dbc6f662dd179","tid":811533,"uid":208074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8eee0a178da3e27384fba924b27490870c8e1a36","tid":811533,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/09/101340_89f6c374beccf878730170970bc5a152.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2F101340_89f6c374beccf878730170970bc5a152.gif&h=4ff45171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n福氣來㗎 香港人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:28:28.000Z","msg":"呢D真係香港人先享受到"},{"pid":"574811486ee38b92914bed46ee71d582902dcf71","tid":811533,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8420bcc688e878de7e5cd90b0b91c9e7f627ea61","tid":811533,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:33:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b54f2a8c0b1ab1286fa5c3b6aae9e42461ee52a","tid":811533,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:35:43.000Z","msg":"真心傻豬"},{"pid":"aea1773ce23f47f042ed252e229d6d346c9a0680","tid":811533,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:39:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"822fe9efc6eff0bce8a88acaf991e671a565a775","tid":811533,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:40:17.000Z","msg":"買咗之後再租俾人做141"},{"pid":"cb82d1b3143392223ee2007c0d2d4484dba44149","tid":811533,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來可以劏開賣"},{"pid":"59ac0b9ccbc7c3823486e2295955af6c68fbc24a","tid":811533,"uid":208074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"822fe9efc6eff0bce8a88acaf991e671a565a775","tid":811533,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:40:17.000Z","msg":"買咗之後再租俾人做141"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:44:02.000Z","msg":"會唔會太細<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d3aaf64aa6f332e73ff89785441aa32a